                    },
                    "body": "From an API perspective, invoking a function of the form \"is_xxx(...)\", I would only expect either a true/false value.\r\n* Are there other boolean functions that return \"null\"? \r\n* Are there other functions that given a \"null\" input, return other than \"null\"?",
